graph TD
    classDef plain fill:transparent,stroke:none,color:#000

    %% Data Input Stage
    subgraph Data Input
        A[ACS Provided Dataset]:::plain --> B[Load Data via pandas]:::plain
    end

    %% Preprocessing Pipeline
    subgraph Preprocessing Pipeline
        B --> C[Missing Value Imputation]:::plain
        C --> D[Feature Encoding]:::plain
        D -->|One-Hot| E[Demographics: Urban/Rural, Water Source]:::plain
        D -->|Ordinal| F[Packaging Type: PET, LDPE, HDPE, Non-Plastic]:::plain
        E & F --> G[Feature Standardization]:::plain
        G --> H[Class Balancing via SMOTE]:::plain
    end

    %% Analysis/Modeling
    subgraph Analysis & Modeling
        H --> I[Train-Test Split]:::plain
        I --> J[XGBoost Classifier]:::plain
        J --> K[Stratified K-Fold Cross Validation]:::plain
        K --> L[Model Evaluation]:::plain
    end

    %% Output Stage
    subgraph Output & Visualization
        L --> M[Feature Importance Plot]:::plain
        L --> N[Confusion Matrix]:::plain
        B --> O[EDA Plots: Distributions & Heatmaps]:::plain
    end
